eficiency of the Laws of England. Soberly Discovered: Or, Liberty Working up to Its Just Height. reprinted in 6 The Harleian Miscellany: 212–225.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Warr%2C%20J.%201810.%20The%20Corruption%20and%20Deficiency%20of%20the%20Laws%20of%20England.%20Soberly%20Discovered%3A%20Or%2C%20Liberty%20Working%20up%20to%20Its%20Just%20Height.%20reprinted%20in%206%20The%20Harleian%20Miscellany%3A%20212%E2%80%93225." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0002_ref_058_w2aab2b8b5b1b7b1ab2ac58Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Wilson, R. 1943. English and French in England 1100–1300. History 28. 37–60.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1468-229X.1943.tb00837.x" class="link link-external doi" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">10.1111/j.1468-229X.1943.tb00837.x</a><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Wilson%2C%20R.%201943.%20English%20and%20French%20in%20England%201100%E2%80%931300.%20History%2028.%2037%E2%80%9360." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="reference" id="j_ijld-2016-0002_ref_059_w2aab2b8b5b1b7b1ab2ac59Aa"><span class="reference-mixed-citation">Wogan-Browne, J. 2009. Introduction. In J. Wogan-Browne (ed.), Language and culture in medieval Britain, 1–13. York: York Medieval Press.</span><span class="newline"></span><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar?q=Wogan-Browne%2C%20J.%202009.%20Introduction.%20In%20J.%20Wogan-Browne%20%28ed.%29%2C%20Language%20and%20culture%20in%20medieval%20Britain%2C%201%E2%80%9313.%20York%3A%20York%20Medieval%20Press." class="link link-external googleScholar" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">Search in Google Scholar</a></p><p class="refer